# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   -> imperative, lower-case, <=72 chars, no period
#
# <body>   -> the WHY, wrapped ~72 chars (optional)
#
# <footer> -> BREAKING CHANGE: ... | Closes #123 (optional)
#
# ---- Conventional Commits — see COMMIT_CONVENTION.md ----
# types:  feat fix refactor style perf test docs build ci chore revert
# scopes: ui form api ai types hooks results config deploy docs
#
# examples:
#   feat(ai): add generate-plan service using OpenAI generateObject
#   fix(api): return 504 on LLM request timeout
#   docs(readme): document required environment variables
